Package: scReports
Type: Package
Title: R Markdown Templates and Functions for the Visualisation of Single Cell Data
Version: 0.2.4
Date: 2023-03-01
Author: Trishanta Padayachee, Eva Adriaensen
Maintainer: Eva Adriaensen <eva.adriaensen@openanalytics.eu>
Description: A collection of functions and templates for the exploration of single cell data. The package currently focuses on the quality control of single cell data. 
